description:
The Pressure Volume Loop Analysis Module extends LabChart to provide the detection and analysis of ventricular pressure and volume data.

The Pressure Volume Loop Analysis Module extends LabChart to provide the detection and analysis of ventricular pressure and volume data. The module calculates and displays a wide range of cardiac function parameters, relationships and plots. The module can be used to analyze pre-recorded data or to analyze data as it is sampled.
- Improve PV Loop workflow layout for non-English regional settings
